        <item>
            <title>Damson 0.3.8</title>
            <description>
                &lt;h3&gt;Fixed&lt;/h3&gt;
                &lt;ul&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Selecting text in a full-screen app (vim, htop, Claude Code, …) no longer nudges the screen up by about half a line.&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;An empty shell prompt no longer scrolls down into blank space below the last line.&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;A small full-screen app no longer has extra scroll room above it — scrolling up now reveals only real history.&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            </description>
            <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 03:49:22 +0000</pubDate>
